:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Fri, 28 Jun 2024 07:46:40 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistics]]></category><category><![CDATA[coronavirus]]></category><category><![CDATA[counting]]></category><category><![CDATA[estimation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Howtown]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=74509 </guid><description><![CDATA[It&#8217;s impossible to know the exact number of Covid deaths worldwide, because consistent&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/coronavirus/" rel="tag">冠状病毒</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/counting/" rel="tag">计数</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/estimation/" rel="tag">估计</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/howtown/" rel="tag">Howtown</a></p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>不可能知道全球新冠死亡的确切人数，因为并不是每个人、每个地方都保存一致的记录。因此研究人员必须进行估计。 Howtown 在下面的视频中解释了各种估算方法。 </p><p class="iframe-container"><iframe class="youtube-player" width="1090" height="614" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JS2rCjvjYLU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox"></iframe></p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/coronavirus/" rel="tag">冠状病毒</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/counting/" rel="tag">计数</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/estimation/" rel="tag">估计</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/howtown/" rel="tag">Howtown</a></p> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 74509</post-id></item><item><title> ✚ 可视化工具和学习资源，2024 年 6 月综述</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/06/27/visualization-tools-and-learning-resources-june-2024-roundup/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:30:33 +0000</pubDate> <c